When you launch this code,little window had opened and little red balls are falling from top to the ground with medium speed.Task of player is score 20 points(this number can de changed in code)
In next updates to that project i create a menu which can help change winning points in game
Task of player is tap on falling balls, if ball reach minimum height game automatically lose,for every ball that player has tapped he take one point,after that ball deleted from scene 
In the left side of game window you can see button "Quit" if you push this button application will close
in the grounded half of application you can see Text "Score" if player made process of pushing to this strophe add 1 point
